{"tid":672589,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳真社: 至7月底資金便會用盡 有多1000人月捐$200 便能延續傳真社使命","createTime":"2018-05-21T06:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T03:11:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":37,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1d68f698fb4062f3e4fec11b7d9cdf830fc047e1","tid":672589,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"加入月捐．撐起真相<br />\n<br />\n過去兩年，傳真社堅持初衷，以公平和不偏不倚的原則尋找真相，一共發表了73篇獨家調查報道。 <br />\n可惜，我們的資金在7月底就會耗盡，倒閉危機迫在眉睫。你，可以拯救傳真社！<br />\n<br />\n傳真社每月經營開支約25萬元，只要有1325名讀者願意月捐200元，就可以延續傳真社的使命。<br />\n<br />\n傳真社至今有300人月捐200元，為我們帶來每月5萬多元的收入。數字一直上升，然而仍未足以應付每月約25萬元的營運開支。<br />\n<br />\n請邀請抱持共同理念的朋友，一同撐起真相！<br />\n<br />\n立即月捐<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/support-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fsupport-us&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=19bd5ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/support-us</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們近期獨家揭發的調查報道<br />\n<br />\n取得5歲女童陳瑞臨死亡前相片<br />\n<br />\n．顯示臨臨上學時已有傷痕 <br />\n<br />\n．與校長說法有出入\t<br />\n<br />\n．揭示校方知情不報<br />\n<br />\n公開南生圍橫水渡遭縱火一刻畫面<br />\n<br />\n． 顯示3時起火兩人目擊火勢<br />\n<br />\n． 警方曾公佈系統沒有錄影 <br />\n<br />\n．促使警方重新大規模調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/backus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Fbackus&d=kmTCRgqU9%2FUFNKzfZ8RYgO9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=df01751e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/backus</a>"},{"pid":"26c72427da69975c94302fa64a2344bf98cc0cc3","tid":672589,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"又捐"},{"pid":"762e48a1c3618065dcb32f841fbd70be88901c10","tid":672589,"uid":48083,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"BTW有得單次捐款<br />\n<br />\n月捐計劃<br />\n每月 $200<br />\n可購買10份公司註冊文件，以解構利益集團的關連，例如樓宇維修公司網絡<br />\n<br />\n每月 $400<br />\n可翻查4份地契文件，協助監察領展停車場、電話機樓用地等土地使用<br />\n<br />\n每月 $600<br />\n可支付一次存取閉路電視的工程費，揭開南生圍縱火、林子健被擄走等事件不為人知的一面<br />\n<br />\n每月 $800<br />\n一年共9600元，可支持我們進行跨地域的調查報道，揭發台山核電安全、高鐵生產商製新加坡列車發現裂紋、劉曉波臨終前一直被扣羈押病房等報道<br />\n<br />\n每月 $1000<br />\n一年共12,000元，可以為我們支付半個月辦公室租金，讓我們在安全、不被滋擾的地方進行調查工作"},{"pid":"389a10e668367e64a64e62e1f8f9fff3a1d73e05","tid":672589,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caedd29c8ea053f36e1ebea77d6b9bdc42d43054","tid":672589,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"26c72427da69975c94302fa64a2344bf98cc0cc3","tid":672589,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"又捐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"當佢NGO"},{"pid":"543131ddebce58e1cb97939ed3f8eade96214031","tid":672589,"uid":25424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"389a10e668367e64a64e62e1f8f9fff3a1d73e05","tid":672589,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:42:08.000Z","msg":"不如叫佢轉做慈善機構算啦<br />\n方便俾人扣稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57ca8a1c7f48248e89ba9c0a95f66496fc1a35c","tid":672589,"uid":104443,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:43:24.000Z","msg":"捐！大家都要捐！唔可以比良心媒體沒落！大家係香港人就要捐！"},{"pid":"e2c083f0d9570a4b8f5e9a3c7ccb27b06ecc137b","tid":672589,"uid":78620,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:45:23.000Z","msg":"傳真社搵料落力過好多報社"},{"pid":"1169e01bd2598c66569619e43bce8cd0b95ab638","tid":672589,"uid":53687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"543131ddebce58e1cb97939ed3f8eade96214031","tid":672589,"uid":25424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"389a10e668367e6